{"tid":1867892,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【本土研究社】不封關之迷：林鄭死都唔封關，因為未來要開更多關!","createTime":"2020-02-07T10:38:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T09:21:19.000Z","uid":138409,"like":177,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":98,"replies":[{"pid":"4da04c76a9171d441c0d4db0fd3b700e9542536f","tid":1867892,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:38:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/videos/212417023218492/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flocalresearch%2Fvideos%2F212417023218492%2F&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwUVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=7a13dd09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/videos/212417023218492/</a><br />\n<br />\n好多人唔明點解連幾千醫護罷工，林鄭死都唔肯全面封關。其實除左係性格問題，好可能係因為同佢配合既大灣區未來「中門大開」既規劃方針背道而馳，過唔到自己「心理關口」。<br />\n<br />\n除左現時14個入境管制站，好多人冇咩留意未來為左配合粵港澳大灣區戰略，重會打通更多其他新關口，有啲本身重係靜靜雞被規劃，隨時成為未來防疫新隱患。<br />\n<br />\n== 大灣區「隱藏關口」大檢閱 ==<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 蓮塘口岸免簽證入境</span>：配合東進東出的深港規劃，本身預左上年開通，因運動同疫情依家暫緩至今年底，但原初規劃文件假設未來俾內地居民免簽證入境。【註一】即係佢未來都諗著有關等於冇關，依家重點會全面封關?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">2. 河套區神秘專才通道</span>：為配合大灣區創科產業融合，河套規劃中暗中劃左有條大橋橫跨深圳河，會成為一個全新過境通道。早幾年官方規劃研究有提及會「有待進一步研究」【註二】，近年就有新聞放風研究緊俾啲「河套證」深港專才直接過境【註三】，甚至研究緊點俾深圳落黎有條「綠色通道」，用人臉辨識技術做到「無感通關」【註四】。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">3. 北環線直接送中</span>：本身規劃中既北環線原意係駁通新界西北到東北，但近月深圳政府已經預留埋個位俾北環線接埋上皇崗超級口岸【註五】，而前規劃署署長上年12月就開始放風話建議北環線變成送中鐵路【註六】，即係暗中違反鐵路策略，又想整多一個類似羅湖既新入境通路。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">4. 粵港澳遊艇自駕遊</span>：好少人知道除左空陸兩路入境，2017年已經開始實施「粵港澳遊艇自由行」，水路都可以直接落黎自駕遊。依家大灣區規劃重研究緊再簡化出入境手續，重配合緊起更多本地遊艇泊位俾陸艇上岸【註七】，例如東大嶼欣澳填海區，遲啲成條海岸線隨時都有入境隱患。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">5. 東大嶼高鐵支線站</span>：早前研究社揭發深圳已規劃東大嶼人工島有條高鐵支線【註八】，好可能市區又割多塊地做一地兩檢內地口岸區，到時有類似疫情叫停高鐵站將會更難自主決策!<br />\n<br />\n所以，未來唔單止關口愈來愈多，關口本身都出現重大變化，邊界會變得愈來愈不確定、滲透性高、更難自主決策，最後更難防疫守護。<br />\n<br />\n內地居民免簽證、專才自出自入、更多一地兩檢、海域邊界模糊化，未來中港邊境藍圖就係想中門大開，「全面封關」當然成為了執政者的心魔。<br />\n<br />\n#今天只關注一件事 #醫護罷工 #全面封關 #大灣區規劃 #隱藏關口 #被規劃 #海陸空路無得避 #邊界政治<br />\n<br />\n--<br />\n【註一】蘋果日報：蓮塘口岸文件驚爆 誓推深圳居民免簽 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2H4yeye\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2H4yeye&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwUVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=7cfae6d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2H4yeye</a><br />\n【註二】本土研究社：被篡改的河套規劃 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2vegOMU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2vegOMU&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwUVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=4bcca5c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2vegOMU</a><br />\n【註三】林鄭：土地確認屬香港 將為深圳人員提供出入境便利 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2OzqCIk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2OzqCIk&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwUVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=cd7074a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2OzqCIk</a><br />\n【註四】大公報：深圳規劃河套深方區域「1+8」政策 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/39gevrq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F39gevrq&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwUVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=2cebc5b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/39gevrq</a><br />\n【註五】蘋果日報：港鐵北環綫「被規劃」越深圳河直達新皇崗 或淪「被送中」新陷阱 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/39lKwP7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F39lKwP7&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwUVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=3324f103\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/39lKwP7</a><br />\n【註六】頭條新聞：凌嘉勤倡北環線伸延 至河套區設新口岸 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2H8jSwJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2H8jSwJ&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwUVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=6681c5c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2H8jSwJ</a><br />\n【註七】文匯報：深圳推海事24舉措 增遊艇自由行試點 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/3bi9n7X\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3bi9n7X&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwUVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=bd18d53b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3bi9n7X</a><br />\n【註八】本土研究社：國家機密洩露：東大嶼人工島有條隱藏高鐵？ <a href=\"http://bit.ly/376COXs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F376COXs&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwUVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=ee48be04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/376COXs</a><br />\n<br />\n--<br />\n🥅支援中港關係研究：<a href=\"https://liber-research.com/research-category/environment-2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2Fresearch-category%2Fenvironment-2%2F&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwUVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=1ea5acb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://liber-research.com/research-category/environment-2/</a><br />\n📸Follow IG：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/liberresearch/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fliberresearch%2F&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwUVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=7318d27f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/liberresearch/</a><br />\n🌎本研TG Channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/liberinfo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fliberinfo&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwUVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=16d6524d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/liberinfo</a><br />\n💰月捐支持民間研究：<a href=\"https://liber-research.com/support-us-2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2Fsupport-us-2%2F&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwUVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=38934b3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://liber-research.com/support-us-2/</a>"},{"pid":"2bacd870e3eb6cd2c9404f250b30a06ccdd34846","tid":1867892,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:40:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a512e4be82814780f48ba0bd0c51904fe1ecea2","tid":1867892,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:43:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal